No. 10-8752 (R46-012). Clay Randolph Shadley, Petitioner v. Earl Grimes, et al. 562 U.S. 1281, 131 S. Ct. 1630,

179 L. Ed. 2d 521,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 2102. March 10, 2011.

The petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit in the above-titled case was dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46.1 of the Rules of this Court.

Same case below, 405 Fed. Appx. 813.
